span.span: Defines and creates generic type parameters for dynamically defined generic types and methods.

summary.span: 此类不能被继承。

span.span: This class cannot be inherited.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 您可以 使用方法来获取对象的数组 ，方法是将类型参数添加到动态类型，从而使其成为泛型类型，或使用 方法将类型参数添加到动态方法。You can get an array of objects by using the method to add type parameters to a dynamic type, thus making it a generic type, or by using the method to add type parameters to a dynamic method. 使用 对象可将约束添加到类型参数。Use the objects to add constraints to the type parameters. 约束分为以下三种类型：Constraints are of three kinds: - 基类型约束指定分配给泛型类型参数的任何类型必须派生自特定基类型。The base type constraint specifies that any type assigned to the generic type parameter must derive from a particular base type. 使用方法设置此约束 。Set this constraint by using the method. - 接口约束指定分配给泛型类型参数的任何类型都必须实现特定接口。An interface constraint specifies that any type assigned to the generic type parameter must implement a particular interface. 使用方法设置接口约束 。Set the interface constraints by using the method. - 特殊约束指定分配给泛型类型参数的任何类型都必须具有无参数的构造函数，必须是引用类型，或者必须是值类型。Special constraints specify that any type assigned to the generic type parameter must have a parameterless constructor, must be a reference type, or must be a value type. 使用方法设置类型参数的特殊约束 。Set the special constraints for a type parameter by using the method. 不能使用类的方法来检索接口约束和特殊约束 。Interface constraints and special constraints cannot be retrieved using methods of the class. 创建包含类型参数的泛型类型后，可以使用其 对象来反映约束。Once you have created the generic type that contains the type parameters, you can use its object to reflect the constraints. 使用 方法获取类型参数，并为每个类型参数使用 方法获取基类型约束和接口约束，并使用 属性来获取特定约束。Use the method to get the type parameters, and for each type parameter use the method to get the base type constraint and interface constraints, and the property to get the special constraints. ## Examples 下面的代码示例创建一个具有两个类型参数的泛型类型，并将它们保存在程序集 GenericEmitExample1.dll 中。The following code example creates a generic type with two type parameters, and saves them in the assembly GenericEmitExample1.dll. 可以使用 [Ildasm.exe (IL 拆装器) ](/dotnet/framework/tools/ildasm-exe-il-disassembler) 查看生成的类型。You can use the [Ildasm.exe (IL Disassembler)](/dotnet/framework/tools/ildasm-exe-il-disassembler) to view the generated types. 有关定义动态泛型类型所涉及步骤的更详细说明，请参阅 [如何：使用反射发出定义泛型类型](/dotnet/framework/reflection-and-codedom/how-to-define-a-generic-type-with-reflection-emit)。For a more detailed explanation of the steps involved in defining a dynamic generic type, see [How to: Define a Generic Type with Reflection Emit](/dotnet/framework/reflection-and-codedom/how-to-define-a-generic-type-with-reflection-emit). remarks.format: ## Remarks 特殊约束可以指定分配给泛型类型参数的任何类型都必须具有无参数的构造函数，必须是引用类型，或者必须是值类型。Special constraints can specify that any type assigned to the generic type parameter must have a parameterless constructor, must be a reference type, or must be a value type. 不能使用类的方法检索特殊约束 。Special constraints cannot be retrieved using methods of the class. 创建包含类型参数的泛型类型后，可以使用其 对象来反映类型参数及其约束。Once you have created the generic type that contains the type parameter, you can use its object to reflect the type parameters and their constraints. 若要获取已完成的泛型类型的类型参数，请使用 方法。To get the type parameters of a completed generic type, use the method. 若要获取每个类型参数的特殊约束，请使用 属性。To get the special constraints for each type parameter, use the property. 引用类型参数的方差特征的枚举值仅适用于支持协变和逆变的语言，如 Microsoft 中间语言 (MSIL) 。The enumeration values that refer to the variance characteristics of a type parameter are relevant only in languages that support covariance and contravariance, such as Microsoft intermediate language (MSIL).
